# -*- mode: org; fill-column:65 -*-

This  is COSE  (celestia open  space engine)  - game  engine  based on
celestia engine.

* Building under Linux, FreeBSD

  Obtain the dependent libraries, then build with:

  #+begin_example
  ./configure
  make
  make install
  #+end_example

* Build under Windows

  No MSVS project files jet.

* Run client

  #+begin_example
  ./openspace_client -g /path/to/celestia's_files
  #+end_example

  

#+TITLE:    COSE
#+STARTUP:  showall
#+OPTIONS:  author:nil title:nil
